$ROL_TRTREL
Rollback
Call ROLL From GLOCK
If GROLL
   Call ECR_TRACE(mess(17,107,1),1) From GESECRAN
Else
  Goto MAJREL
Endif
Return

$AB_TRTREL
Rollback
